oai_dc:dc.dc:title: A novel approach to tricyclo[6.2.2.0(1,6)]dodecanes through tandem Diels-Alder reactions
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: HADIMANI, SB
PADMAKUMAR, R
MANISEKARAN, T
BHAT, SV
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: convenient synthesis
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: One-pot synthesis of tricyclo[6.2.2.0(1,6)]dodecane skeleton 5 has been achieved through the Diels-Alder reaction of methyl beta-(5,5-dimethyl-2-oxocyclohexa-1,3-dien-1-yl)acrylate 2 with ethyl vinyl ether.
oai_dc:dc.dc:identifier: INDIAN JOURNAL OF CHEMISTRY SECTION B-ORGANIC CHEMISTRY INCLUDING MEDICINAL CHEMISTRY, 36(5), 381-383
